    "description": "<p>LBD ENGINEERING PTE. LTD.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLBD Engineering Pte Ltd, as one of the home-grown building contractors in Singapore, we have come a long way throughout the years. As the Group continues to focus actively on viable diversification, we also strive to strengthen our core businesses in building and civil engineering.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Currently, we are involved with both Architectural and Structural sub-contract works of several public institutional and residential projects, civil engineering and interior design businesses. The Group is also embarking on expanding further to upgrade its capacity and participating in tendering of both private and public projects.<br />\r\n </p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n </p>\r\n",
